{"tid":2372158,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國一名男子在芝加哥機場禁區生活3個月才被發現","createTime":"2021-01-19T12:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T12:07:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f6aa412a863ffb7145edadc26bd399018242fd1f","tid":2372158,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571256-20210119.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571256-20210119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmek4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=c0546959\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571256-20210119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dc229b3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571256-20210119.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國加州一名男子，聲稱因為害怕新型肺炎疫情不敢回家，在芝加哥機場禁區生活3個月，直至幾日前才被發現。<br />\n<br />\n36歲的辛格去年10月19日從洛杉磯抵達芝加哥的奧黑爾國際機場，大部分時間留在機場禁區，靠乘客送贈的食物維生。兩名聯合航空職員於上星期六發現辛格，要求查看證件，辛格出示一張偷來的營運經理證件後被揭發，職員隨即報警。<br />\n<br />\n辛格被捕後被控擅入機場禁區及盜竊罪名，獲准保釋，但禁止再踏足機場。辛格沒有案底，報稱無業，向警方表示因害怕疫情不敢回家。暫時未知他前往芝加哥的目的。"},{"pid":"24fae7bf19180835fe7a3490f77db006becbae4a","tid":2372158,"uid":34456,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"機場客運站"},{"pid":"7194ebc315968ff7682527f24f6c05a48c7d7ba8","tid":2372158,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"被人發現<br />\n<br />\n我諗都只係武肺 小人<br />\n<br />\n平時人山人海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df3e3f8bc31e26c1d7583570cccbbb42fcba3da","tid":2372158,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24fae7bf19180835fe7a3490f77db006becbae4a","tid":2372158,"uid":34456,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"機場客運站"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T12:07:1